name: MFAXII - Hand Over My Life To Another Misconception
description:
I thought I was free from the lies, but then it was nothing.
Not for a long time, I realized it was just another mistake I made,
dressed to impress others.
Beneath every title, I made nothing but regret,
promises don't look so cool anymore.
Being an imposter to myself, wasted in every weekend, overcome my body, neglected my mind, poisoning my own blood.
Suddenly got blurred by my own overstatement.
